### **9. ПРИЛОЖЕНИЕ: СХЕМА ИМЕН ПОРТОВ**

| Тип узла | Входные порты | Выходные порты |
|----------|---------------|----------------|
| Literal | — | `output` |
| Math (Add, Subtract, Multiply, Divide, Modulo) | `inputA`, `inputB` | `output` |
| Compare (Equal, Greater, Less, GreaterOrEqual, LessOrEqual, NotEqual) | `left`, `right` | `result` |
| Logical (And, Or) | `left`, `right` | `result` |
| Not | `input` | `result` |
| If | `condition` | `true`, `false` |
| VariableGet | — | `value` |
| VariableSet | `name`, `value` | `output` |
| DebugLog | `message`, `execute` | `output` |

